Setup
-----
The following uses my clj script: http://github.com/joeyates/bash-clj/raw/master/clj

$ git clone git://github.com/joeyates/sloccount-clojure.git
$ clj --cp classes
user=> (compile 'sloccount)     
sloccount
user=> [Ctrl+d]

Use
---
$ clj --cp classes --run sloccount

